special_description = "Combine medium assault tank. Boyar Cannon is a direct-fire AP shell tuned for anti-medium engagements — flat trajectory + sharp accuracy. Secondary Coaxial MG covers close infantry. Branches retune the gun: Dozer trades the cannon for a rocket battery (anti-heavy + structures, fire rate ramps on a sustained target); Plow swaps it for a long-range mortar (anti-light, arcs over terrain)."
